# Technical SEO — shared

One responsive URL (mobile-first index). Test **both** Lighthouse mobile + desktop.

- `robots.ts` + `sitemap.ts` + `pageMetadata({ path })` canonical on every page
- `noIndex`: 404, `?q=` on listings (canonical stays base path)
- JSON-LD: `WebPageSchema` + type schema; `inLanguage: ur`
- Server-rendered primary content; no orphan URLs

